    <item>
      <title>Hugo Live Reload</title>
      <link>http://echorand.me/linux_voice_4/post/hugo-live-reload/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 May 2016 09:20:03 +1000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://echorand.me/linux_voice_4/post/hugo-live-reload/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hugo has a live reload feature which means, the moment I save this page, not only is my site content
regenerated, but the browser also reloads the site. This means, I can see my new post without
needing to refresh the site myself.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
